snippet.title: Johnny Depp Fans Can't Believe Amber is in "ZACK SYNDER'S JUSTICE LEAGUE" | Flixet
snippet.description:
In today's video, we will be discussing why Johnny Depp fans are kind of shocked after they hear the news that Amber Heard is in "ZACK SYNDER'S JUSTICE LEAGUE". 

SUBSCRIBE FOR MORE : http://bit.ly/32rc7vI
________________________________________________

Amber Heard clearly doesn't care that she is one of the internet's least favorite people. The actress has found her word being poured over, scrutinized in the majority of cases as her bitter split from Johnny Depp continues to rage in courtrooms on both sides of the Atlantic, while fans try to have her forcibly removed from the DCEU's AQUAMAN 2.

Track: Odessa — LiQWYD & Scandinavianz
